            "timeouts": null,
            "user_data": "#!/bin/bash\n\n# Update system and install nginx\nsudo apt update -y\nsudo apt install nginx -y\nsudo systemctl start nginx\nsudo systemctl enable nginx\n\n# Create a simple landing page\ncat \u003c\u003cEOF | sudo tee /var/www/html/index.nginx-debian.html\n\u003c!DOCTYPE html\u003e\n\u003chtml lang=\"en\"\u003e\n\u003chead\u003e\n\u003cmeta charset=\"UTF-8\"\u003e\n\u003cmeta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"\u003e\n\u003ctitle\u003ePrateek's Terraform Server\u003c/title\u003e\n\n\u003cstyle\u003e\nbody{\n    margin:0;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    background: linear-gradient(120deg,#1e3c72,#2a5298);\n    color:white;\n    text-align:center;\n}\n\n.container{\n    margin-top:120px;\n}\n\nh1{\n    font-size:40px;\n}\n\np{\n    font-size:20px;\n}\n\nbutton{\n    padding:12px 25px;\n    font-size:16px;\n    border:none;\n    border-radius:6px;\n    background:#ffcc00;\n    cursor:pointer;\n}\n\nbutton:hover{\n    background:#ffaa00;\n}\n\n.footer{\n    position:fixed;\n    bottom:10px;\n    width:100%;\n    font-size:14px;\n}\n\u003c/style\u003e\n\n\u003c/head\u003e\n\n\u003cbody\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003e🚀 Welcome to My Terraform Server\u003c/h1\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\nHi, I'm \u003cb\u003ePrateek\u003c/b\u003e.  \nThis EC2 instance was automatically deployed using\n\u003cb\u003eTerraform Infrastructure as Code\u003c/b\u003e.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp id=\"time\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbutton onclick=\"showMessage()\"\u003eClick Me\u003c/button\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"footer\"\u003e\nBuilt with AWS EC2 + Terraform\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\nfunction showMessage(){\n    alert(\"Hello from your EC2 server deployed using Terraform!\");\n}\n\nfunction updateTime(){\n    const now = new Date();\n    document.getElementById(\"time\").innerHTML =\n        \"Server Time: \" + now.toLocaleString();\n}\n\nsetInterval(updateTime,1000);\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e\nEOF\n",
